description: Coefficient for quadratic effect of sea surface temperature on COTS growth trigger
enhanced_semantic_description: Captures non-linear impact of temperature extremes on triggering COTS outbreaks

description: Log half-saturation constant for coral dependency in COTS growth, representing resource limitation
enhanced_semantic_description: Controls the degree to which available coral cover (fast + slow) limits the intrinsic growth rate of COTS; lower values imply stronger limitation when coral cover is low
